long: SELECT "e"."employee_id" AS "Employee", "e"."first_name" AS "FirstName", "e"."last_name" AS "LastName", "e"."email" AS "Email", "e"."phone_number" AS "Phone", "e"."salary" AS "Salary", "e"."commission_pct" AS "Commission", "j"."job_title" AS "JobTitle", "d"."department_name" AS "Department", "dm"."first_name" AS "ManagerFirst", "dm"."last_name" AS "ManagerLast", "l"."street_address" AS "Address", "l"."postal_code" AS "Postal", "l"."city" AS "City", "l"."state_province" AS "State", "c"."country_name" AS "Country", "r"."region_name" AS "Region", "jh"."job_id" AS "HistoryJobID", "jh"."start_date" AS "StartDate", "jh"."end_date" AS "EndDate", "jj"."job_title" AS "HistJobTitle", "dd"."department_name" AS "HistDept", CASE WHEN 1 THEN 1 WHEN 2 THEN 2 WHEN 3 THEN 3 WHEN 4 THEN 4 WHEN 5 THEN 5 ELSE 0 END AS "Flag" FROM "employees" AS "e" JOIN "jobs" AS "j" ON "e"."job_id" = "j"."job_id" LEFT JOIN "employees" AS "m" ON "e"."manager_id" = "m"."employee_id" LEFT JOIN "departments" AS "d" ON "d"."department_id" = "e"."department_id" LEFT JOIN "employees" AS "dm" ON "d"."manager_id" = "dm"."employee_id" LEFT JOIN "locations" AS "l" ON "d"."location_id" = "l"."location_id" LEFT JOIN "countries" AS "c" ON "l"."country_id" = "c"."country_id" LEFT JOIN "regions" AS "r" ON "c"."region_id" = "r"."region_id" LEFT JOIN "job_history" AS "jh" ON "e"."employee_id" = "jh"."employee_id" LEFT JOIN "jobs" AS "jj" ON "jj"."job_id" = "jh"."job_id" LEFT JOIN "departments" AS "dd" ON "dd"."department_id" = "jh"."department_id" WHERE "e"."salary" > 5000 AND "d"."department_name" IN ('Sales', 'Marketing', 'IT') ORDER BY "e"."employee_id"

(SELECT "region"."r_regionkey" AS "r_regionkey", "region"."r_name" AS "r_name" FROM "region" AS "region" WHERE "region"."r_name" = 'EUROPE') SELECT "supplier"."s_acctbal" AS "s_acctbal", "supplier"."s_name" AS "s_name", "nation"."n_name" AS "n_name", "part"."p_partkey" AS "p_partkey", "part"."p_mfgr" AS "p_mfgr", "supplier"."s_address" AS "s_address", "supplier"."s_phone" AS "part" WHERE "part"."p_size" = 15 AND "part"."p_type" LIKE '%BRASS') AS "part" LEFT JOIN (SELECT MIN("partsupp"."ps_supplycost") AS "_col_0", "partsupp"."ps_partkey" AS "_u_1" FROM "_e_0" AS "partsupp" CROSS JOIN "_e_1" AS "region" JOIN (SELECT "nation"."n_nationkey" AS "n_nationkey", "nation"."n_regionkey" AS "n_regionkey" FROM "nation" AS "nation") AS "nation" ON "nation"."n_regionkey" = "region"."r_regionkey" JOIN (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_nationkey" AS "s_nationkey" FROM "supplier" AS "supplier") AS "supplier" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey" AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey" GROUP BY "partsupp"."ps_partkey") AS "_u_0" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "_u_0"."_u_1" CROSS JOIN "_e_1" AS "region" JOIN (SELECT "region"."r_regionkey" JOIN "_e_0" AS "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey" JOIN (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name" AS "s_name", "supplier"."s_address" AS "s_address", "supplier"."s_nationkey" AS "s_nationkey", "supplier"."s_phone" AS "s_phone", "supplier"."s_acctbal" AS "s_acctbal", "supplier"."s_comment" AS "s_comment" FROM "supplier" AS "supplier") AS "supplier" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey" AND "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey" WHERE "partsupp"."ps_supplycost" = "_u_0"."_col_0" AND transpile_postgres_to_mysql: SELECT "col" FROM "tbl" WHERE "x" ILIKE '%test%' AND "id" IN (SELECT "id" FROM "other" WHERE "status" = 'active')
transpile_tpch_to_bigquery: WITH cte AS (SELECT "a"."id" AS "id", "a"."name" AS "name", SUM("b"."amount") AS "total" FROM "orders" AS "a" JOIN "line_items" AS "b" ON "a"."id" = "b"."order_id" WHERE "a"."status" = 'complete' GROUP BY "a"."id", "a"."name" HAVING SUM("b"."amount") > 1000) SELECT "cte"."id", "cte"."name", "cte"."total", CAST("cte"."total" AS TEXT) AS "total_str" FROM "cte" ORDER BY "cte"."total" DESC LIMIT 50
